======================================================================
BOUNDARY OF CANCELLATION CHAINS IN Z₂
======================================================================

Pattern: Ω₃ cancellation chains → boundary in Ω₂
  just as Ω₂ cancellation chains → boundary in Ω₁

This is a TELESCOPING structure across dimensions:
  dim p cancellation = pairs of p-paths sharing same bad (p-1)-face
  dim p+1 cancellation fills dim p cancellation cycles


